@CoffeeChainManagement.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:8080

### Health check
GET {{CoffeeChainManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Dashboard overview
GET {{CoffeeChainManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/overview
Accept: application/json

### Branch list
GET {{CoffeeChainManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/branches
Accept: application/json

### Product list
GET {{CoffeeChainManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products
Accept: application/json
